00:16:27.751 --> 00:16:32.521
How can you go from living under ISIS rule to living in a Western democracy?

00:16:33.851 --> 00:16:37.741
If the answer is “you can’t”, then what is the answer?

00:16:39.231 --> 00:16:46.301
